  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Lock, load, click.</strong><br>ClickShot is a trigger-happy clicker where every tap fires your way to cosmetic gun upgrades and massive multipliers. Rack up shells, unlock a growing arsenal, and flex your custom loadout with flashy sights, muzzles, and lasers.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔫 <i>Click your gun</i> to earn shells and cash in on upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 Unlock and equip cosmetics that boost your shell multiplier</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛠 Visit the Workbench to mix ‘n match sights, muzzles, and lasers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💼 Shop for new gear — everything you buy sticks with you permanently</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐢 Lightweight and snappy — perfect for short bursts or long grinds<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655710/extras/72456cf46eec47c68a35ab1ab7a70161.poster.avif?t=1769014056\" width=530 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655710/extras/72456cf46eec47c68a35ab1ab7a70161.webm?t=1769014056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
